---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Customers" description="HelixGitpx is open source; the hosted Service has not launched.">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-semibold">Customers</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-slate-600">
      HelixGitpx is an open-source project (Apache-2.0 / CC-BY-SA-4.0). The
      hosted Service has not launched, so there are no hosted customers today.
      Teams self-hosting from the GA release tag are the project's users; we
      don't collect telemetry and don't track who deploys it.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-12 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 p-8">
        <div class="text-xl font-semibold">Self-hosters</div>
        <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600">Anyone can pull the GA tag and run the full stack from <code>impl/helixgitpx-platform/</code>. Case studies and testimonials will be collected here from teams willing to share.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 p-8">
        <div class="text-xl font-semibold">Early hosted users</div>
        <p class="mt-2 text-slate-600">There is no hosted Service yet, no beta, and no waitlist. Contact the maintainer through GitHub if you want to help launch one.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="mt-16 text-sm text-slate-500">
      If you ship HelixGitpx in production and want to be listed here, open an
      issue on
      <a href="https://github.com/HelixDevelopment/HelixGitpx/issues" class="text-primary hover:underline">GitHub</a>.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
